# Attack On Frightside — Farley Sweet, 2015 (ASL 550), "A Neo Scary God-Game"
# No published walkthrough exists — derived from game source (game.aslx).
# Ending: `hug jimmy` in the Throne Room — the redemption ending (Jimmy
# renounces his curse, the tower falls, Frightside is saved, "FIN") — chosen
# over the alternative `fight jimmy` finish. Both call finish; the hug is the
# game's thematic point ("the power a hug can have on a hurt soul").
# Chain: `kick cell door` breaks out; Piece of Candy (Scary Godmother's
# kitchen) pays the tavern bouncer ("pay bouncer with piece of candy"); the
# bartender's free first round is the Jar of Milk; the milk revives the blue
# monster Bug-a-boo at the Tower Gate, who breaks the gate and eats Chocolate
# Magma; `push fat jimmie` out the window; Aigee PeAitch is spared with
# `mercy aigee peaitch` (kill/duel/mercy all work — mercy fits the ending).
# Flavour speaks included; all deterministic. No score/RNG/timers.
